 47	// the merge below to discharge.
 48	//
 49	// `Storage.layerOptional` is ALSO provided standalone here — a legit second
 50	// consumer (the `/admin` editor's write path: save-draft / publish / image
 51	// upload, plus any route that reads `Storage` directly). It is a separate
 52	// instance from the one inside `Content.defaultLayer`; both point at the same
 53	// bucket via `Env`, so there is no shared in-memory state to coordinate. The
 54	// admin write surface is only *reachable* when `Auth` is enabled
 55	// (`ADMIN_PASSWORD` + `COOKIE_SECRET` set), independent of the bucket; the
 56	// editor still surfaces a `StorageError` when an admin is configured without a
